(37, 2, '2022-02-26 18:49:34', '2022-02-26 10:49:34', '<p>On the other hand, the botanical sense of \"fruit\" includes many structures that are not commonly called \"fruits\", such as bean pods, corn kernels, wheat grains, and tomatoes.</p><p>Some vegetables can be consumed raw, while some, such as cassava, must be cooked to destroy certain natural toxins or microbes in order to be edible.</p><p>But with the blast shield down, I can\'t even see!</p><p>The MacBook Pro is a line of Macintosh portable computers introduced in January 2006 by Apple Inc., and now in its third generation.</p><p>In your time, yes, but nowadays shut up!</p>', 'Cushion', '<p>But with the blast shield down, I can\'t even see!</p>', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'cushion', '', '', '2022-02-26 18:49:34', '2022-02-26 10:49:34', '', 0, 'http://localhost/website/corsivalab-exam/product/cushion/', 0, 'product', '', 0),
