(49, 2, '2022-02-26 18:49:37', '2022-02-26 10:49:37', '<p>It\'s more like ... suicide.</p><p>Besides, these are adult stemcells, harvested from perfectly healthy adults whom I killed for their stemcells.</p><p>The nose?</p>', 'Green Fire Mixer', '<p></p><p>Besides, these are adult stemcells, harvested from perfectly healthy adults whom I killed for their stemcells.</p>', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'green-fire-mixer', '', '', '2022-02-26 18:49:37', '2022-02-26 10:49:37', '', 0, 'http://localhost/website/corsivalab-exam/product/green-fire-mixer/', 0, 'product', '', 0),
