(51, 2, '2022-02-26 18:49:37', '2022-02-26 10:49:37', '<p>A number of processed food items available on the market contain vegetable ingredients and can be referred to as \"vegetable derived\" products.</p><p>I want to know what happened to the plans they sent you.</p><p>The MacBook Pro is a line of Macintosh portable computers introduced in January 2006 by Apple Inc., and now in its third generation.</p><p>Itaque earum rerum hic tenetur a sapiente delectus.</p><p>Why do you think that she is a witch?</p>', 'Yellow Silver Smoothie', '<p>The MacBook Pro is a line of Macintosh portable computers introduced in January 2006 by Apple Inc., and now in its third generation.</p><p>A number of processed food items available on the market contain vegetable ingredients and can be referred to as \"vegetable derived\" products.</p>', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'yellow-silver-smoothie', '', '', '2022-02-26 18:49:37', '2022-02-26 10:49:37', '', 0, 'http://localhost/website/corsivalab-exam/product/yellow-silver-smoothie/', 0, 'product', '', 0),
